5.5 What You'll Be Able to Do
By the end of the programme, you'll be able to:
	•	Explain blockchain technology clearly to both technical and non-technical audiences.
	•	Identify blockchain opportunities relevant to your organisation or business.
	•	Evaluate when blockchain is the right solution — and when it isn't.
	•	Understand how blockchain products are designed and brought to market.
	•	Analyse real-world blockchain use cases across business and social impact.
	•	Make informed decisions about blockchain adoption within your organisation.
	•	Collaborate more effectively with developers, product teams, and technology partners on blockchain initiatives.
